name: Vicky Villas
description: The house has 3 Bedrooms and houses up to 8 People. Around the house is a large Terrace with Barbecue grill and outdoor dining area. The house has large windows to the ground, large patio surrounding the lodge, Barbecue grill, Hard Wood floor, designed lighting and latest modern design with advanced and greenest floor heating system installed in houses today. The house is designed by one of our best architects, Sigurður Hallgrímsson who designed many of our spectacular modern houses in Iceland.
